posting_body: ['NEW 5BD/3BA Townhouse in GREAT Uptown Location!', 'Available 9/1!', 'Property Address', '1723 Lagoon Ave - 1723 (Front Lower) | Minneapolis, MN 55408', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Perkins Levin Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'We are currently running a leasing special of 1 MONTH FREE for a 12 month lease or 2 MONTHS FREE for a 22-23 month lease.', 'This property was constructed in 2021 and this unit will be available for a September move-in date.', 'This unit features high-end design, finishes, hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances and an UNBEATABLE Uptown location just a block from the lakes.', 'There are many other great things you will love about this property, including:', '-Open Kitchen & Living room floor plan w/ Hardwood floors', '-Beautiful Kitchen w/ granite counters, tile back-splash & stainless steel appliances', '-Big bedrooms & LOTS of closet space', '-A Porch', '-Private Laundry', '-3 FULL Bathrooms', '-Central AC/Forced Heat', '-Lots of Windows & Natural Light', '-Pet Friendly (Pet Rent $50/mo.)', '-Premium Uptown Location', '-Professional Management & Maintenance Staff (handles Lawn Care & Snow Removal)', '-Online Rent Payment System', 'Water/Trash/Sewage Utility =', 'Flat rate $125/month, tenants also responsible for gas and electric.', 'For QUESTIONS or a TOUR contact Alex at', 'show contact info', '(text/email preferred).', 'Amenities', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Professional Maintenance', 'Professional Management', 'Online Rent Pay', 'Porch', 'Pet Friendly', 'Central Air', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 5BD/3.0BA', 'Square Feet: 2,395', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $3,195.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $3,195.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
